   IR-Slave 1.1

   (C) 1994 by J³rgen Frank und Michael Watzl

   The IR-Slave is freely distributable in the unregistered version.
The schematics for the hardare and the layout may not be freely
distributed.

   Note: The IR-Slave is shareware. To use the IR-Slave you need the
hardware. See @{"Hardware" Link "Hardware"}. If you want to use the IR-Slave you have to
register. See @{"Registering" Link "Registering"}.

   You use the IR-Slave on your own risk. No warranty can be given.


